[Student "S"]
{NORTH is 1 point too strong to open 1NT, so opens 1\C.

SOUTH responds in his 4-card Major suit, 1\S.

NORTH now shows her 4-card support plus her extra strength by jumping to 3\S and SOUTH bids the game.}

